Dialogue: 0,0:02:11.54,0:02:13.65,Reimi,Reimi,0,0,0,,哇 好厉害！
Dialogue: 0,0:02:14.23,0:02:16.00,Reimi,Reimi,0,0,0,,看看这些水！
Dialogue: 0,0:02:16.00,0:02:17.48,Reimi,Reimi,0,0,0,,这就是高丽川吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:02:17.48,0:02:20.55,Reimi,Reimi,0,0,0,,吾野外面 现在是这样子啊
Dialogue: 0,0:02:20.55,0:02:22.18,Akira,Akira,0,0,0,,真是松懈啊
Dialogue: 0,0:02:22.18,0:02:23.07,Reimi,Reimi,0,0,0,,喂！
Dialogue: 0,0:02:23.07,0:02:24.74,Reimi,Reimi,0,0,0,,晶你真够扫兴的
Dialogue: 0,0:02:25.06,0:02:26.96,Reimi,Reimi,0,0,0,,其实你很兴奋吧
Dialogue: 0,0:02:26.96,0:02:29.09,Reimi,Reimi,0,0,0,,不表现在脸上我也看不出来啊
Dialogue: 0,0:02:29.09,0:02:31.18,Akira,Akira,0,0,0,,怎么可能会兴奋
Dialogue: 0,0:02:31.18,0:02:32.34,Akira,Akira,0,0,0,,突然就出发了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:32.65,0:02:34.26,Akira,Akira,0,0,0,,你那是什么手势？
Dialogue: 0,0:02:34.78,0:02:35.73,Akira,Akira,0,0,0,,不要
Dialogue: 0,0:02:35.94,0:02:37.03,Akira,Akira,0,0,0,,别过来！
Dialogue: 0,0:02:37.14,0:02:39.17,Reimi,Reimi,0,0,0,,我挠挠挠……
Dialogue: 0,0:02:39.60,0:02:41.83,Nadeshiko,Nadeshiko,0,0,0,,真是的 你们两个
Dialogue: 0,0:02:39.60,0:02:41.83,annotation,Sign,0,0,0,,或许是因为过去发生了什么\N抚子非常不喜欢冲突
