Dialogue: 0,0:02:45.81,0:02:47.48,Reimi,Reimi,0,0,0,,喂 什么时候能到池袋？
Dialogue: 0,0:02:47.48,0:02:48.27,Reimi,Reimi,0,0,0,,明天能到吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:02:48.58,0:02:50.62,Akira,Akira,0,0,0,,即使是黑豹车队也到不了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:02:50.78,0:02:52.08,Akira,Akira,0,0,0,,明天是不可能的
Dialogue: 0,0:02:52.22,0:02:52.92,Reimi,Reimi,0,0,0,,诶
Dialogue: 0,0:02:52.92,0:02:55.46,Reimi,Reimi,0,0,0,,但是以前一个小时出头就能到了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:02:55.64,0:02:57.56,Reimi,Reimi,0,0,0,,就算现在被拉长了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:57.84,0:02:59.43,Reimi,Reimi,0,0,0,,那也没什么大不了的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:02:59.56,0:03:00.68,Akira,Akira,0,0,0,,你太乐观了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:00.76,0:03:03.14,Akira,Akira,0,0,0,,这种松懈的态度可到不了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:03.29,0:03:06.05,Akira,Akira,0,0,0,,肯定会在半路上全军覆没的
Dialogue: 0,0:03:06.17,0:03:06.91,Reimi,Reimi,0,0,0,,那个啊
Dialogue: 0,0:03:07.02,0:03:11.37,Reimi,Reimi,0,0,0,,有的时候只要迈出第一步\N忽然就会发现已经快到了哦
Dialogue: 0,0:03:11.50,0:03:13.12,Reimi,Reimi,0,0,0,,一天不行的话那就三天
Dialogue: 0,0:03:13.33,0:03:14.61,Akira,Akira,0,0,0,,不可能
Dialogue: 0,0:03:14.74,0:03:17.60,Akira,Akira,0,0,0,,至少也要一个月 甚至更多
Dialogue: 0,0:03:17.85,0:03:18.70,Reimi,Reimi,0,0,0,,那就半个月
Dialogue: 0,0:03:18.78,0:03:19.50,Akira,Akira,0,0,0,,三个月！
Dialogue: 0,0:03:19.76,0:03:22.54,Reimi,Reimi,0,0,0,,对了 静留肯定也想过这些
Dialogue: 0,0:03:22.68,0:03:23.60,Reimi,Reimi,0,0,0,,问问她吧
Dialogue: 0,0:03:23.74,0:03:25.36,Reimi,Group,0,0,0,,喂 还要多{\4c&HE0C7AC&}长时间？
Dialogue: 0,0:03:24.89,0:03:26.15,Shizuru,Shizuru,0,0,0,,{\an8}别来烦我 很危险的！
Dialogue: 0,0:03:26.65,0:03:29.92,Nadeshiko,Nadeshiko,0,0,0,,好了 静留毕竟才刚会开电车
Dialogue: 0,0:03:30.14,0:03:30.77,Nadeshiko,Nadeshiko,0,0,0,,是吧？
Dialogue: 0,0:03:35.53,0:03:37.85,Nadeshiko,Nadeshiko,0,0,0,,静留 是不是开得有点太快了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:41.45,0:03:43.36,Nadeshiko,Nadeshiko,0,0,0,,果然还是太快了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:03:43.56,0:03:45.19,Nadeshiko,Nadeshiko,0,0,0,,稍微降点速吧
Dialogue: 0,0:03:45.37,0:03:46.28,Shizuru,Shizuru,0,0,0,,在降了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:46.28,0:03:46.88,Nadeshiko,Nadeshiko,0,0,0,,诶？
Dialogue: 0,0:03:47.29,0:03:49.65,Shizuru,Shizuru,0,0,0,,虽然在降了 但速度没有下来
Dialogue: 0,0:03:49.80,0:03:51.41,Default,Group,0,0,0,,诶——
Dialogue: 0,0:03:52.79,0:03:53.59,Reimi,Reimi,0,0,0,,弯！
Dialogue: 0,0:03:53.59,0:03:55.17,Akira,Akira,0,0,0,,转弯！转弯！
Dialogue: 0,0:03:55.74,0:03:57.60,Akira,Akira,0,0,0,,还是转弯
Dialogue: 0,0:03:58.62,0:04:00.67,Reimi,Reimi,0,0,0,,转弯……
Dialogue: 0,0:04:02.72,0:04:03.68,Nadeshiko,Nadeshiko,0,0,0,,急转弯
Dialogue: 0,0:04:04.01,0:04:07.74,Default,Group,0,0,0,,转弯——
Dialogue: 0,0:04:09.02,0:04:11.36,annotation,Sign,0,0,0,,受到7G的影响\N本该在高崎观音山\N山顶的高崎观音\N移动到了高丽川
Dialogue: 0,0:04:16.86,0:04:18.51,Akira,Akira,0,0,0,,还以为要死了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:18.72,0:04:20.32,annotation,Sign,0,0,0,,即memento mori
Dialogue: 0,0:04:18.73,0:04:20.32,Akira,Akira,0,0,0,,正所谓「凡人终有一死啊」
Dialogue: 0,0:04:20.69,0:04:22.90,Nadeshiko,Nadeshiko,0,0,0,,嘛 没事吗 静留
Dialogue: 0,0:04:23.09,0:04:23.97,Shizuru,Shizuru,0,0,0,,大概吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:24.45,0:04:28.66,Shizuru,Shizuru,0,0,0,,善治郎先生教我的时候 看上去更简单呢
Dialogue: 0,0:04:29.17,0:04:30.48,Nadeshiko,Nadeshiko,0,0,0,,善治郎先生？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:30.70,0:04:31.81,Shizuru,Shizuru,0,0,0,,他能恢复正常了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:31.92,0:04:33.75,Shizuru,Shizuru,0,0,0,,虽然一天只有五分钟就是了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:33.86,0:04:34.53,Shizuru,Shizuru,0,0,0,,就是那时候他教我的
Dialogue: 0,0:04:34.84,0:04:35.38,Reimi,Reimi,0,0,0,,诶？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:35.49,0:04:36.14,Akira,Akira,0,0,0,,这不可能
Dialogue: 0,0:04:36.22,0:04:38.33,Shizuru,Shizuru,0,0,0,,不是 真的啦真的 还是个帅老头
Dialogue: 0,0:04:38.40,0:04:39.34,Akira,Group,0,0,0,,帅{\4c&HDEC8F4&}老头{\4c&HE0C7AC&}？！{\4c&HDEC8F4&}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:39.44,0:04:41.11,Nadeshiko,Nadeshiko,0,0,0,,撒谎可不行哦 静留
Dialogue: 0,0:04:41.16,0:04:45.12,Shizuru,Shizuru,0,0,0,,不 真的是真的啦！不然我是怎么会开电车的
Dialogue: 0,0:04:45.29,0:04:48.17,Shizuru,Shizuru,0,0,0,,善治郎先生以前是铁路公司的精英对吧？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:48.29,0:04:50.23,Akira,Akira,0,0,0,,我还以为只是谣言来着
Dialogue: 0,0:04:50.42,0:04:51.22,Reimi,Reimi,0,0,0,,原来是真的吗
Dialogue: 0,0:04:51.49,0:04:53.57,Nadeshiko,Nadeshiko,0,0,0,,「只能变回去五分钟」是指？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:53.70,0:04:55.60,Shizuru,Shizuru,0,0,0,,他不是有个帽子吗？铁路的那个
Dialogue: 0,0:04:55.73,0:04:57.05,Shizuru,Shizuru,0,0,0,,给他戴上就变回去了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:57.18,0:04:58.94,Nadeshiko,Nadeshiko,0,0,0,,那个啊 静留
Dialogue: 0,0:04:59.06,0:05:00.88,Nadeshiko,Nadeshiko,0,0,0,,说谎真的不好哦
Dialogue: 0,0:05:00.88,0:05:03.14,Shizuru,Shizuru,0,0,0,,真的真的！真的是真的！
Dialogue: 0,0:05:03.14,0:05:05.06,Shizuru,Shizuru,0,0,0,,不然我怎么会开列车的！
Dialogue: 0,0:05:05.13,0:05:06.17,Shizuru,Shizuru,0,0,0,,相信我啊！
Dialogue: 0,0:05:06.34,0:05:09.54,Reimi,Reimi,0,0,0,,说起来 真的要去池袋对吧？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:09.73,0:05:11.12,Reimi,Reimi,0,0,0,,没走错方向吧？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:11.22,0:05:11.73,Akira,Akira,0,0,0,,哈？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:12.69,0:05:14.29,Shizuru,Shizuru,0,0,0,,那边是秩父对吧？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:14.57,0:05:16.60,Shizuru,Shizuru,0,0,0,,所以这边是池袋
Dialogue: 0,0:05:16.74,0:05:18.17,Reimi,Reimi,0,0,0,,哦原来如此
Dialogue: 0,0:05:18.30,0:05:19.21,Akira,Akira,0,0,0,,原来如此？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:19.41,0:05:23.07,Reimi,Reimi,0,0,0,,池袋有找模特的星探还有执事对吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:23.17,0:05:25.67,Reimi,Reimi,0,0,0,,还有侦探和杀人犯
Dialogue: 0,0:05:25.80,0:05:29.00,Reimi,Reimi,0,0,0,,不注意的话 就会被捅 被拐走 被骗吧！
Dialogue: 0,0:05:29.24,0:05:31.39,Reimi,Reimi,0,0,0,,鸡皮疙瘩都起来了 但是好潮！
Dialogue: 0,0:05:31.57,0:05:33.39,Akira,Akira,0,0,0,,你这是什么刻板印象
Dialogue: 0,0:05:33.54,0:05:35.09,Reimi,Reimi,0,0,0,,你也注意别被骗了哦
Dialogue: 0,0:05:35.21,0:05:35.58,Akira,Akira,0,0,0,,诶？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:35.77,0:05:36.59,Akira,Akira,0,0,0,,玲实 你有钱吗
Dialogue: 0,0:05:36.82,0:05:39.24,Reimi,Reimi,0,0,0,,当然有了！我可一直在存钱
Dialogue: 0,0:05:39.33,0:05:39.86,Reimi,Reimi,0,0,0,,啊！
Dialogue: 0,0:05:40.08,0:05:41.53,Shizuru,Shizuru,0,0,0,,真好啊 你有多少
Dialogue: 0,0:05:41.60,0:05:42.94,Reimi,Reimi,0,0,0,,{\an8}我的存钱罐！
Dialogue: 0,0:05:42.82,0:05:43.72,Shizuru,Shizuru,0,0,0,,两万日元有吗
Dialogue: 0,0:05:42.82,0:05:43.72,annotation,Sign,0,0,0,,差不多一千块人民币
Dialogue: 0,0:05:43.97,0:05:45.86,Reimi,Reimi,0,0,0,,不！我的存钱罐——
Dialogue: 0,0:05:45.86,0:05:47.37,Nadeshiko,Nadeshiko,0,0,0,,玲实她怎么了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:05:46.68,0:05:49.06,Reimi,Reimi,0,0,0,,{\an8}我把存钱罐留在家里了…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:47.46,0:05:49.26,Akira,Akira,0,0,0,,啊 她家里有个存钱罐来着
Dialogue: 0,0:05:49.49,0:05:50.83,Reimi,Reimi,0,0,0,,我只有250日元
Dialogue: 0,0:05:49.49,0:05:50.83,annotation,Sign,0,0,0,,差不多12元人民币
Dialogue: 0,0:05:50.93,0:05:51.53,Akira,Akira,0,0,0,,好少！
Dialogue: 0,0:05:51.77,0:05:54.12,Reimi,Reimi,0,0,0,,晶你呢 那晶你又带了多少啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:54.34,0:05:56.48,Akira,Akira,0,0,0,,个人情报不容透露
Dialogue: 0,0:05:56.69,0:05:57.96,Reimi,Reimi,0,0,0,,借我钱啦
Dialogue: 0,0:05:57.96,0:05:59.74,Akira,Akira,0,0,0,,恕不外借
Dialogue: 0,0:05:59.88,0:06:00.87,Reimi,Reimi,0,0,0,,小气鬼！
Dialogue: 0,0:06:01.06,0:06:03.50,Shizuru,Shizuru,0,0,0,,我有不少钱 借你们也可以哦
Dialogue: 0,0:06:03.62,0:06:06.37,Reimi,Reimi,0,0,0,,真的吗！静留你真是神！能借我多少
Dialogue: 0,0:06:06.48,0:06:09.19,Shizuru,Shizuru,0,0,0,,我带了差不多三千日元 所以借一千吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:09.28,0:06:09.95,Default,Group,0,0,0,,好{\4c&HDEC8F4&}少！
Dialogue: 0,0:06:10.08,0:06:11.30,Shizuru,Shizuru,0,0,0,,不是吧！已经很多了吧！
Dialogue: 0,0:06:11.50,0:06:12.66,Reimi,Reimi,0,0,0,,这种状况该怎么形容来着
Dialogue: 0,0:06:12.76,0:06:14.69,Reimi,Reimi,0,0,0,,「没面包的话 为什么不吃蛋糕呢」？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:14.97,0:06:16.50,Nadeshiko,Nadeshiko,0,0,0,,感觉不太对
Dialogue: 0,0:06:16.64,0:06:18.30,Akira,Akira,0,0,0,,「两害相权取其轻」
Dialogue: 0,0:06:18.30,0:06:19.81,Reimi,Reimi,0,0,0,,对对 就是这种感觉
Dialogue: 0,0:06:19.90,0:06:20.94,Akira,Akira,0,0,0,,才不是感觉吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:21.02,0:06:23.77,Reimi,Reimi,0,0,0,,1250日元吗～买什么好呢～
Dialogue: 0,0:06:23.77,0:06:25.36,Nadeshiko,Nadeshiko,0,0,0,,首先要买食物吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:25.44,0:06:27.49,Reimi,Reimi,0,0,0,,啊 我想喝珍珠奶茶
Dialogue: 0,0:06:27.57,0:06:30.58,Reimi,Reimi,0,0,0,,还有shurushururi啦 法式吐司啦…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:27.57,0:06:30.58,annotation,Sign,0,0,0,,实际上是奇克美露里\N格鲁吉亚的传统炖烤鸡\N监督在松屋吃过\N
Dialogue: 0,0:06:30.64,0:06:32.38,Nadeshiko,Nadeshiko,0,0,0,,不是啦 我说的是更普通的食物
Dialogue: 0,0:06:32.49,0:06:34.03,Nadeshiko,Nadeshiko,0,0,0,,罐头或者干面包什么的
Dialogue: 0,0:06:34.13,0:06:37.00,Reimi,Reimi,0,0,0,,诶！那多无聊 抚子你没有梦想吗
Dialogue: 0,0:06:37.08,0:06:39.49,Nadeshiko,Nadeshiko,0,0,0,,但是 我们毕竟什么都没带嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:06:39.62,0:06:40.15,Reimi,Reimi,0,0,0,,诶？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:40.30,0:06:42.20,Nadeshiko,Nadeshiko,0,0,0,,我们不是从学校直接来的嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:06:43.09,0:06:44.34,Reimi,Reimi,0,0,0,,真的耶
Dialogue: 0,0:06:44.64,0:06:46.06,Reimi,Reimi,0,0,0,,什么吃的都没有啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:46.18,0:06:47.70,Shizuru,Shizuru,0,0,0,,食物的话倒是有一点
Dialogue: 0,0:06:47.80,0:06:48.81,Reimi,Reimi,0,0,0,,真的吗？好耶！
Dialogue: 0,0:06:48.89,0:06:49.69,Nadeshiko,Nadeshiko,0,0,0,,为啥？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:49.81,0:06:51.52,Shizuru,Shizuru,0,0,0,,那我肯定要做准备的嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:06:51.66,0:06:52.59,Akira,Akira,0,0,0,,能看看吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:52.70,0:06:53.44,Shizuru,Shizuru,0,0,0,,嗯 可以哦
Dialogue: 0,0:06:53.62,0:06:57.20,Akira,Akira,0,0,0,,果然野外生存就要做好最低限度的准备和…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:57.64,0:06:59.33,Akira,Akira,0,0,0,,这是什么？坐禅时敲的东西？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:59.58,0:07:00.70,Reimi,Reimi,0,0,0,,你不知道吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:00.80,0:07:02.33,Reimi,Reimi,0,0,0,,这是做意面的东西啊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:02.46,0:07:04.24,Akira,Akira,0,0,0,,所以哪里有意面啦！
Dialogue: 0,0:07:04.41,0:07:05.85,Akira,Akira,0,0,0,,这不是《练马之国的爱丽丝》里的小苏吗！
Dialogue: 0,0:07:04.41,0:07:08.43,annotation,Sign,0,0,0,,小苏的su来自于suicide(自杀)\N所以脖子上有根绳子\N是和主角人气二分的主要角色
Dialogue: 0,0:07:05.97,0:07:06.60,Reimi,Reimi,0,0,0,,真的耶！
Dialogue: 0,0:07:06.70,0:07:08.43,Reimi,Reimi,0,0,0,,为什么静留你带着？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:08.60,0:07:10.39,Shizuru,Shizuru,0,0,0,,哦 我在家找到的
Dialogue: 0,0:07:09.02,0:07:10.39,Akira,Akira,0,0,0,,{\an8}抚子 让我看看
Dialogue: 0,0:07:10.49,0:07:11.68,Reimi,Reimi,0,0,0,,我也要！我也要！
Dialogue: 0,0:07:11.76,0:07:12.24,Shizuru,Shizuru,0,0,0,,也行啦…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:12.24,0:07:12.93,Akira,Akira,0,0,0,,不行！
Dialogue: 0,0:07:12.97,0:07:13.66,Reimi,Reimi,0,0,0,,她给我了嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:07:13.66,0:07:15.81,Nadeshiko,Nadeshiko,0,0,0,,不要吵架！好好相处
Dialogue: 0,0:07:15.98,0:07:19.06,Nadeshiko,Nadeshiko,0,0,0,,静留 食物就只有这些哦
Dialogue: 0,0:07:19.20,0:07:19.84,Shizuru,Shizuru,0,0,0,,诶？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:20.37,0:07:22.62,Shizuru,Shizuru,0,0,0,,我还以为带了更多的
Dialogue: 0,0:07:22.72,0:07:23.75,Nadeshiko,Nadeshiko,0,0,0,,还有那些
Dialogue: 0,0:07:23.75,0:07:24.90,Shizuru,Shizuru,0,0,0,,哦 苦瓜？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:25.05,0:07:29.42,annotation,Sign,0,0,0,,静留不喜欢苦瓜\N是因为吃太多了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:25.05,0:07:26.85,Shizuru,Shizuru,0,0,0,,我知道苦瓜是吾野名产啦
Dialogue: 0,0:07:27.00,0:07:29.42,Shizuru,Shizuru,0,0,0,,但不是特别喜欢呢
Dialogue: 0,0:07:30.02,0:07:32.24,Shizuru,Shizuru,0,0,0,,呃啊！我到底干了些什么！
Dialogue: 0,0:07:32.40,0:07:34.71,Shizuru,Shizuru,0,0,0,,太兴奋了 都搞不清楚状况了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:34.71,0:07:36.45,Akira,Akira,0,0,0,,啊 是有这样的时候啦
Dialogue: 0,0:07:36.52,0:07:38.14,Akira,Akira,0,0,0,,注意不到周围环境了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:07:38.26,0:07:40.00,Reimi,Reimi,0,0,0,,偏偏是这个时候发作了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:40.18,0:07:42.02,Nadeshiko,Nadeshiko,0,0,0,,之前列个清单就好了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:07:43.02,0:07:43.99,Nadeshiko,Nadeshiko,0,0,0,,那个…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:44.45,0:07:47.44,Nadeshiko,Nadeshiko,0,0,0,,这些就是我们的全部财产了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:48.97,0:07:50.52,Shizuru,Shizuru,0,0,0,,有个问题
Dialogue: 0,0:07:50.73,0:07:51.58,Default,Group,0,0,0,,问题？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:51.98,0:07:53.37,Shizuru,Shizuru,0,0,0,,内裤啊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:53.65,0:07:54.28,Reimi,Reimi,0,0,0,,这个问题？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:54.28,0:07:55.09,Akira,Akira,0,0,0,,内裤吗…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:55.21,0:07:57.78,Nadeshiko,Nadeshiko,0,0,0,,女孩子不能说内…的啦！
Dialogue: 0,0:07:57.84,0:07:58.66,Shizuru,Shizuru,0,0,0,,那就裤衩
Dialogue: 0,0:07:58.66,0:07:59.69,Nadeshiko,Nadeshiko,0,0,0,,才不是这样的吧！
Dialogue: 0,0:07:59.76,0:08:03.09,Akira,Akira,0,0,0,,但是实际上 也不知道要多久才会到池袋
Dialogue: 0,0:08:03.16,0:08:04.57,Reimi,Reimi,0,0,0,,那我们只能穿这些衣服了？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:04.69,0:08:06.61,Akira,Akira,0,0,0,,据说卡斯蒂利亚王国的伊莎贝尔一世
Dialogue: 0,0:08:06.68,0:08:10.72,Akira,Akira,0,0,0,,为了祈祷胜利 九个月没换过内裤
Dialogue: 0,0:08:10.80,0:08:13.04,Shizuru,Shizuru,0,0,0,,如果我也不换的话 是不是就能找到叶香呢
Dialogue: 0,0:08:13.16,0:08:14.80,Nadeshiko,Nadeshiko,0,0,0,,静留你冷静点！
Dialogue: 0,0:08:14.96,0:08:16.17,Shizuru,Shizuru,0,0,0,,诶？啊…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:16.36,0:08:18.54,Akira,Akira,0,0,0,,到东吾野的时候买点吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:18.62,0:08:20.84,Nadeshiko,Nadeshiko,0,0,0,,食物也要储存一些呢
Dialogue: 0,0:08:20.96,0:08:22.04,Nadeshiko,Nadeshiko,0,0,0,,买点保质期长的
Dialogue: 0,0:08:22.16,0:08:23.85,Reimi,Reimi,0,0,0,,肚子饿了——好痛！
Dialogue: 0,0:08:24.05,0:08:24.95,Akira,Akira,0,0,0,,你想死吗
Dialogue: 0,0:08:25.12,0:08:28.00,Akira,Akira,0,0,0,,生存恐怖片里 只想吃饭的胖子\N总是第一个死的
Dialogue: 0,0:08:28.08,0:08:28.93,Reimi,Reimi,0,0,0,,我才不是胖子！
Dialogue: 0,0:08:29.00,0:08:31.40,Nadeshiko,Nadeshiko,0,0,0,,稍微忍忍吧 就现在
Dialogue: 0,0:08:31.72,0:08:33.62,Reimi,Reimi,0,0,0,,忍耐吗？我可不擅长
Dialogue: 0,0:08:34.96,0:08:37.70,Reimi,Reimi,0,0,0,,你肯定要说「玲实最不会忍耐」吧！
Dialogue: 0,0:08:37.89,0:08:40.86,Akira,Akira,0,0,0,,啊～啊 被抢词了 真是肚子里的蛔虫啊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:40.97,0:08:41.70,Reimi,Reimi,0,0,0,,你说什么呢！
Dialogue: 0,0:08:41.70,0:08:42.72,Nadeshiko,Nadeshiko,0,0,0,,冷静点
Dialogue: 0,0:08:50.29,0:08:51.98,Reimi,Reimi,0,0,0,,还没到池袋吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:52.34,0:08:54.15,Akira,Akira,0,0,0,,你怎么老是问这个
Dialogue: 0,0:08:54.30,0:08:56.17,Reimi,Reimi,0,0,0,,怎么了 我很在意嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:08:56.49,0:08:58.06,Akira,Akira,0,0,0,,你脑子不好吗
Dialogue: 0,0:08:59.26,0:09:02.51,Reimi,Reimi,0,0,0,,这样高高在上的你性格可真坏
Dialogue: 0,0:09:02.65,0:09:04.49,Reimi,Reimi,0,0,0,,爱哭鬼鼻涕虫晶！
Dialogue: 0,0:09:04.60,0:09:07.61,Akira,Akira,0,0,0,,爱哭鬼是十多年前的事了吧！
Dialogue: 0,0:09:07.61,0:09:08.30,Reimi,Reimi,0,0,0,,哼！
Dialogue: 0,0:09:08.37,0:09:09.81,Akira,Akira,0,0,0,,零分玲实灵长类！
Dialogue: 0,0:09:09.88,0:09:11.60,Reimi,Reimi,0,0,0,,我就得过一次零蛋！
Dialogue: 0,0:09:11.65,0:09:12.64,Reimi,Reimi,0,0,0,,再说那只是小测试！
Dialogue: 0,0:09:12.72,0:09:14.49,Nadeshiko,Nadeshiko,0,0,0,,真是的 你们俩别吵了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:14.57,0:09:16.93,Akira,Akira,0,0,0,,那么不愿意的话 你待在吾野就好了嘛！
Dialogue: 0,0:09:17.05,0:09:19.70,Reimi,Reimi,0,0,0,,我又没说不愿意！不要擅自替我决定
Dialogue: 0,0:09:18.83,0:09:21.26,Nadeshiko,Nadeshiko,0,0,0,,{\an8}晶 玲实
Dialogue: 0,0:09:19.72,0:09:21.77,Reimi,Reimi,0,0,0,,不是晶你自己要上车的嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:09:21.92,0:09:24.62,Akira,Akira,0,0,0,,你和抚子不上的话我才不来呢
Dialogue: 0,0:09:24.72,0:09:27.42,Nadeshiko,Nadeshiko,0,0,0,,那时候 该说是没思考就做了决定吗
Dialogue: 0,0:09:27.60,0:09:28.61,Nadeshiko,Nadeshiko,0,0,0,,大家都是吧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:28.69,0:09:30.68,Shizuru,Shizuru,0,0,0,,你们没必要硬跟着来的
Dialogue: 0,0:09:33.93,0:09:36.30,Shizuru,Shizuru,0,0,0,,我本来就打算一个人的
Dialogue: 0,0:09:38.52,0:09:40.46,Reimi,Reimi,0,0,0,,事先说明 静留你啊…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:44.55,0:09:46.07,Nadeshiko,Nadeshiko,0,0,0,,苦瓜？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:46.37,0:09:48.66,Reimi,Reimi,0,0,0,,感觉苦瓜是不是比平时长得还快
Dialogue: 0,0:09:49.22,0:09:51.06,Akira,Akira,0,0,0,,还有 雾也很大
Dialogue: 0,0:09:51.28,0:09:52.51,Reimi,Reimi,0,0,0,,这里是哪？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:52.69,0:09:55.04,Akira,Akira,0,0,0,,我们不会已经路过东吾野了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:10:05.98,0:10:07.75,Shizuru,Shizuru,0,0,0,,玲实 你视力很好对吧？
Dialogue: 0,0:10:07.90,0:10:09.35,Shizuru,Shizuru,0,0,0,,那边能看到什么吗
Dialogue: 0,0:10:09.53,0:10:10.93,Reimi,Reimi,0,0,0,,什么 你要说鬼故事吗
Dialogue: 0,0:10:11.05,0:10:12.12,Nadeshiko,Nadeshiko,0,0,0,,那边 说的是…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:12.77,0:10:15.11,Reimi,Reimi,0,0,0,,嗯什么呢 我也没看到什么…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:15.40,0:10:16.12,Reimi,Reimi,0,0,0,,诶？
Dialogue: 0,0:10:16.29,0:10:17.00,Reimi,Reimi,0,0,0,,那是什么？
Dialogue: 0,0:10:17.24,0:10:17.81,Akira,Akira,0,0,0,,什么？！
Dialogue: 0,0:10:18.12,0:10:19.25,Reimi,Reimi,0,0,0,,有什么东西来了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:19.38,0:10:20.58,Nadeshiko,Nadeshiko,0,0,0,,「什么东西」是什么？
Dialogue: 0,0:10:20.68,0:10:21.59,Reimi,Reimi,0,0,0,,那是…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:21.66,0:10:22.61,Akira,Akira,0,0,0,,高丽川水怪啊！
Dialogue: 0,0:10:22.68,0:10:23.56,Default,Group,0,0,0,,高丽川水怪？
Dialogue: 0,0:10:23.77,0:10:27.15,Akira,Akira,0,0,0,,在高丽川生存至今的长颈龙！
Dialogue: 0,0:10:23.77,0:10:27.15,annotation,Sign,0,0,0,,是7G前的谣言 真假未知\N车站有卖它的周边食物
Dialogue: 0,0:10:31.34,0:10:32.10,Shizuru,Shizuru,0,0,0,,啊
Dialogue: 0,0:10:32.82,0:10:33.98,Shizuru,Shizuru,0,0,0,,真的是高丽川水怪
Dialogue: 0,0:10:36.54,0:10:38.20,Shizuru,Shizuru,0,0,0,,真的是高丽川水怪…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:48.98,0:10:51.37,Default,Swan Hermit,0,0,0,,是电车吗 那个
Dialogue: 0,0:10:53.23,0:10:55.71,Default,Swan Hermit,0,0,0,,你们是谁？
Dialogue: 0,0:10:55.85,0:10:56.71,Akira,Akira,0,0,0,,小心！
Dialogue: 0,0:10:56.82,0:10:58.80,Akira,Akira,0,0,0,,绝对是要来杀我们的杀手！
Dialogue: 0,0:10:58.92,0:10:59.47,Default,Swan Hermit,0,0,0,,正是！
Dialogue: 0,0:10:59.56,0:11:03.10,Default,Swan Hermit,0,0,0,,我正是被称作高丽川连环杀手的…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:03.20,0:11:04.69,Default,Swan Hermit,0,0,0,,喂！很失礼的吧！
Dialogue: 0,0:11:08.81,0:11:10.85,Shizuru,Shizuru,0,0,0,,那个 你是哪位…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:10.85,0:11:12.92,Default,Swan Hermit,0,0,0,,名字什么的根本无所谓！
Dialogue: 0,0:11:15.41,0:11:18.32,Default,Swan Hermit,0,0,0,,呀嘛 那个 我是 怎么说呢…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:18.66,0:11:22.86,Default,Swan Hermit,0,0,0,,我沿着高丽川溯流而上 做了不少记录和调查
Dialogue: 0,0:11:23.09,0:11:26.06,Default,Swan Hermit,0,0,0,,好久没遇到人了 吓了我一跳
Dialogue: 0,0:11:26.14,0:11:28.26,Default,Swan Hermit,0,0,0,,总之 你们是来干什么的
Dialogue: 0,0:11:28.41,0:11:31.22,Shizuru,Shizuru,0,0,0,,那个…我们打算去池袋
Dialogue: 0,0:11:31.35,0:11:33.54,Default,Swan Hermit,0,0,0,,诶 池袋吗？那真厉害
Dialogue: 0,0:11:33.72,0:11:35.42,Default,Swan Hermit,0,0,0,,我就是从池袋来的
Dialogue: 0,0:11:33.72,0:11:35.42,annotation,Sign,0,0,0,,其实他来自\N池袋站隔壁的要町站
Dialogue: 0,0:11:35.48,0:11:36.46,Default,Swan Hermit,0,0,0,,你们的勇猛果敢…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:36.46,0:11:37.24,Shizuru,Shizuru,0,0,0,,真的吗！
Dialogue: 0,0:11:37.68,0:11:39.61,Shizuru,Shizuru,0,0,0,,从池袋来的？好厉害！
Dialogue: 0,0:11:39.72,0:11:41.71,Default,Swan Hermit,0,0,0,,呀 倒也没那么…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:41.81,0:11:44.39,Shizuru,Shizuru,0,0,0,,我还是第一次遇到池袋来的人！
Dialogue: 0,0:11:44.50,0:11:45.64,Default,Swan Hermit,0,0,0,,啊 这样吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:11:45.81,0:11:48.20,Reimi,Reimi,0,0,0,,你知道西武吗？东武呢？中池袋公园呢？
Dialogue: 0,0:11:48.32,0:11:49.71,Reimi,Reimi,0,0,0,,池巴士呢？Animate呢？
Dialogue: 0,0:11:49.76,0:11:51.52,Akira,Akira,0,0,0,,淳久堂书店呢？三省堂书店呢？
Dialogue: 0,0:11:51.56,0:11:52.57,Reimi,Reimi,0,0,0,,还有珍珠奶茶！
Dialogue: 0,0:11:52.69,0:11:54.15,Reimi,Reimi,0,0,0,,现在最有人气的咖啡厅呢？
Dialogue: 0,0:11:54.50,0:11:55.47,Default,Swan Hermit,0,0,0,,谁知道呢…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:55.57,0:11:56.46,Reimi,Reimi,0,0,0,,「谁知道呢」是怎样啦！
Dialogue: 0,0:11:56.46,0:11:57.46,Reimi,Reimi,0,0,0,,他不知道啊
Dialogue: 0,0:11:58.42,0:11:59.43,Default,Swan Hermit,0,0,0,,等等！
Dialogue: 0,0:11:59.54,0:12:02.74,Default,Swan Hermit,0,0,0,,但有一件事是确定的！应该能这么说吧
Dialogue: 0,0:12:02.90,0:12:04.06,Shizuru,Shizuru,0,0,0,,诶？是什么
Dialogue: 0,0:12:04.50,0:12:06.49,Default,Swan Hermit,0,0,0,,那就是7G事件之后
Dialogue: 0,0:12:06.58,0:12:10.35,Default,Swan Hermit,0,0,0,,西武池袋线之外的世界全都消失了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:10.35,0:12:11.01,Shizuru,Shizuru,0,0,0,,诶？！
Dialogue: 0,0:12:11.14,0:12:14.21,Default,Swan Hermit,0,0,0,,我想我大概是这么推测的
Dialogue: 0,0:12:14.37,0:12:16.84,Shizuru,Shizuru,0,0,0,,推测 大概 想？
Dialogue: 0,0:12:16.84,0:12:17.82,Shizuru,Shizuru,0,0,0,,到底是哪个啊！
Dialogue: 0,0:12:17.82,0:12:20.63,annotation,Sign,0,0,0,,监督说看似天鹅仙人疯人疯语\N回头来看会有不一样的体验
Dialogue: 0,0:12:17.82,0:12:20.63,Default,Swan Hermit,0,0,0,,东边的菌类生长得超过头顶
Dialogue: 0,0:12:20.73,0:12:22.69,Default,Swan Hermit,0,0,0,,堂而皇之地宣言要发起征服
Dialogue: 0,0:12:22.69,0:12:24.17,Default,Swan Hermit,0,0,0,,再往东边去
Dialogue: 0,0:12:24.17,0:12:28.63,Default,Swan Hermit,0,0,0,,和山羊共存 与兽无异 猪突猛进的那些人…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:28.63,0:12:29.85,Reimi,Reimi,0,0,0,,所以你到底想说什么
Dialogue: 0,0:12:29.85,0:12:30.59,Reimi,Reimi,0,0,0,,你在说什么呢
Dialogue: 0,0:12:30.59,0:12:31.42,Akira,Akira,0,0,0,,是那个吧
Dialogue: 0,0:12:31.42,0:12:33.32,Akira,Akira,0,0,0,,对荒诞派戏剧的独白的拙劣模仿
Dialogue: 0,0:12:33.32,0:12:34.24,Nadeshiko,Nadeshiko,0,0,0,,啊 这样吗
Dialogue: 0,0:12:34.24,0:12:36.50,Nadeshiko,Nadeshiko,0,0,0,,所以看上去这么夸张啊
Dialogue: 0,0:12:36.50,0:12:37.74,Shizuru,Shizuru,0,0,0,,我们该走了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:37.74,0:12:38.33,Default,Swan Hermit,0,0,0,,诶？
Dialogue: 0,0:12:38.50,0:12:40.25,Default,Swan Hermit,0,0,0,,诶 等等！等等等等啊！
Dialogue: 0,0:12:40.25,0:12:44.40,Default,Swan Hermit,0,0,0,,总之我想说的是 不推荐去池袋 就是这样！
Dialogue: 0,0:12:44.40,0:12:45.39,Shizuru,Shizuru,0,0,0,,为什么？
Dialogue: 0,0:12:45.53,0:12:49.87,Default,Swan Hermit,0,0,0,,总之我推测会遇上可怕 很可怕 不可思议的事
Dialogue: 0,0:12:50.08,0:12:51.32,Shizuru,Shizuru,0,0,0,,你是这么觉得的
Dialogue: 0,0:12:51.65,0:12:52.34,Default,Swan Hermit,0,0,0,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:12:53.09,0:12:53.66,Shizuru,Shizuru,0,0,0,,好 我们走吧
Dialogue: 0,0:12:53.84,0:12:54.63,Default,Swan Hermit,0,0,0,,喂等等！
Dialogue: 0,0:12:55.22,0:12:57.74,Default,Swan Hermit,0,0,0,,来都来了 给点东西吧
Dialogue: 0,0:12:57.97,0:12:59.84,Default,Swan Hermit,0,0,0,,拜托了——
Dialogue: 0,0:13:01.13,0:13:02.80,Default,Swan Hermit,0,0,0,,我会给你们好东西作为交换！好东西！
Dialogue: 0,0:13:02.94,0:13:03.67,Default,Swan Hermit,0,0,0,,来交换吧！
Dialogue: 0,0:13:03.67,0:13:04.67,Shizuru,Shizuru,0,0,0,,好东西？
Dialogue: 0,0:13:04.96,0:13:06.64,Default,Swan Hermit,0,0,0,,这个 我自制的地图
Dialogue: 0,0:13:06.78,0:13:07.86,Default,Swan Hermit,0,0,0,,肯定会超有用的啦
Dialogue: 0,0:13:08.00,0:13:09.13,Default,Swan Hermit,0,0,0,,我非常推荐哦！
Dialogue: 0,0:13:09.32,0:13:10.35,Shizuru,Shizuru,0,0,0,,啊 谢了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:10.44,0:13:11.56,Default,Swan Hermit,0,0,0,,还有一句建议
Dialogue: 0,0:13:11.70,0:13:13.08,Default,Swan Hermit,0,0,0,,什么都不要相信
Dialogue: 0,0:13:13.28,0:13:13.80,Shizuru,Shizuru,0,0,0,,哈？
Dialogue: 0,0:13:14.13,0:13:16.81,Default,Swan Hermit,0,0,0,,能相信的只有自己确信的东西
Dialogue: 0,0:13:16.94,0:13:18.56,Default,Swan Hermit,0,0,0,,啊我说的就另当别论了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:18.94,0:13:19.88,Shizuru,Shizuru,0,0,0,,自己？
Dialogue: 0,0:13:22.08,0:13:24.65,Akira,Akira,0,0,0,,废话连篇说的就是这种人吧
Dialogue: 0,0:13:24.93,0:13:27.18,Default,Swan Hermit,0,0,0,,啊好伤人啊！别说啊
Dialogue: 0,0:13:27.28,0:13:28.17,Nadeshiko,Nadeshiko,0,0,0,,静留
Dialogue: 0,0:13:28.33,0:13:29.75,Nadeshiko,Nadeshiko,0,0,0,,这个给他也没关系吧
Dialogue: 0,0:13:29.75,0:13:30.69,Nadeshiko,Nadeshiko,0,0,0,,是你父亲的东西吧
Dialogue: 0,0:13:31.08,0:13:32.38,Nadeshiko,Nadeshiko,0,0,0,,我们又不需要
Dialogue: 0,0:13:31.08,0:13:32.38,annotation,Sign,0,0,0,,这里neta了\N现实品牌iqos专用的\NMarlboro牌烟弹
Dialogue: 0,0:13:32.49,0:13:33.20,Default,Swan Hermit,0,0,0,,呀！呀呀！
Dialogue: 0,0:13:33.46,0:13:36.26,Default,Swan Hermit,0,0,0,,这不正是文明的结晶 加热烟！
Dialogue: 0,0:13:36.36,0:13:37.66,Default,Swan Hermit,0,0,0,,的烟弹嘛！
Dialogue: 0,0:13:33.46,0:13:37.66,annotation,Sign,0,0,0,,监督说他其实没有加热器\N多半之后会烧着吸
Dialogue: 0,0:13:37.78,0:13:39.46,Shizuru,Shizuru,0,0,0,,嗯这个就行的话那就给你了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:39.46,0:13:42.46,Default,Swan Hermit,0,0,0,,谢谢你！Merci! Grazie! {\fnMicrosoft Sans Serif}ขอบคุณค่ะ!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:39.46,0:13:42.46,annotation,Sign,0,0,0,,分别是日语、法语、意大利语、泰语的「谢谢」
Dialogue: 0,0:13:42.57,0:13:43.78,Shizuru,Shizuru,0,0,0,,真的不客气
Dialogue: 0,0:13:43.92,0:13:45.44,Shizuru,Shizuru,0,0,0,,小心点哦老爷子
Dialogue: 0,0:13:45.44,0:13:46.59,Default,Swan Hermit,0,0,0,,交给我吧
Dialogue: 0,0:13:46.76,0:13:47.98,Default,Swan Hermit,0,0,0,,我会沿着高丽川溯流而上
Dialogue: 0,0:13:48.06,0:13:50.53,Default,Swan Hermit,0,0,0,,对西武池袋线沿线展开探险！
Dialogue: 0,0:13:50.53,0:13:52.48,Default,Swan Hermit,0,0,0,,解开所有的谜题
Dialogue: 0,0:13:52.56,0:13:53.59,Default,Swan Hermit,0,0,0,,诶 等等
Dialogue: 0,0:13:53.78,0:13:55.59,Default,Swan Hermit,0,0,0,,我才不是「老爷子」啊！
Dialogue: 0,0:13:55.70,0:13:56.99,Default,Swan Hermit,0,0,0,,我还很年轻的啊——
Dialogue: 0,0:13:58.02,0:13:59.55,Reimi,Reimi,0,0,0,,真是个怪人啊
Dialogue: 0,0:13:59.72,0:14:02.61,Nadeshiko,Nadeshiko,0,0,0,,但是我们也好久没遇到新的人类大人了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:02.61,0:14:03.94,Nadeshiko,Nadeshiko,0,0,0,,除了猫哥他们
Dialogue: 0,0:14:04.16,0:14:05.48,Akira,Akira,0,0,0,,哦 确实
Dialogue: 0,0:14:05.94,0:14:08.95,Shizuru,Shizuru,0,0,0,,感觉他像那种兜售护身符的
Dialogue: 0,0:14:08.95,0:14:11.52,Reimi,Reimi,0,0,0,,啊 我懂的 他不仅可疑还像是在说谎
Dialogue: 0,0:14:11.71,0:14:14.95,Shizuru,Shizuru,0,0,0,,我还是第一次遇到比善治郎先生还怪的人
Dialogue: 0,0:14:15.14,0:14:18.34,Akira,Akira,0,0,0,,说起来 为什么善治郎先生不和我们一起来呢
Dialogue: 0,0:14:18.54,0:14:20.06,Reimi,Reimi,0,0,0,,诶才不要呢 和他一起什么的
Dialogue: 0,0:14:20.06,0:14:21.06,Reimi,Reimi,0,0,0,,要让他睡哪儿啊
Dialogue: 0,0:14:21.13,0:14:23.74,Akira,Akira,0,0,0,,我们现在讨论的可不是这么肤浅的问题啊
Dialogue: 0,0:14:23.88,0:14:26.60,Akira,Akira,0,0,0,,如果一起走的话 就能问他很多问题吧
Dialogue: 0,0:14:26.74,0:14:30.12,Shizuru,Shizuru,0,0,0,,善治郎先生说他不想 也没法离开吾野
Dialogue: 0,0:14:30.32,0:14:31.20,Reimi,Reimi,0,0,0,,为啥？
Dialogue: 0,0:14:31.36,0:14:35.77,Shizuru,Shizuru,0,0,0,,他说自己离开吾野 就会头晕头疼得厉害
Dialogue: 0,0:14:35.89,0:14:38.36,Shizuru,Shizuru,0,0,0,,说是因为喵喵手术才会这样
Dialogue: 0,0:14:35.89,0:14:38.36,annotation,Sign,0,0,0,,监督说是7G和手术的共同作用
Dialogue: 0,0:14:38.52,0:14:39.92,Akira,Akira,0,0,0,,这不会是心理暗示吧？
Dialogue: 0,0:14:40.09,0:14:41.02,Nadeshiko,Nadeshiko,0,0,0,,心理暗示是什么？
Dialogue: 0,0:14:41.17,0:14:43.00,Nadeshiko,Nadeshiko,0,0,0,,洗脑或是催眠术那种？
Dialogue: 0,0:14:43.02,0:14:43.75,Akira,Akira,0,0,0,,对
Dialogue: 0,0:14:43.85,0:14:47.32,Akira,Akira,0,0,0,,喵喵状态可能只是一种心理暗示
Dialogue: 0,0:14:47.54,0:14:49.32,Akira,Akira,0,0,0,,说不定他其实没任何问题
Dialogue: 0,0:14:49.60,0:14:52.58,Shizuru,Shizuru,0,0,0,,但他额头上确实有伤疤啊
Dialogue: 0,0:14:52.73,0:14:54.19,Akira,Akira,0,0,0,,嗯 那倒也是
Dialogue: 0,0:14:54.37,0:14:57.77,Reimi,Reimi,0,0,0,,嘛总之 我想说的是 善治郎先生不在真是太好了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:57.94,0:14:59.34,Nadeshiko,Nadeshiko,0,0,0,,玲实你真是
Dialogue: 0,0:14:59.49,0:15:02.00,Shizuru,Shizuru,0,0,0,,多一个人的话食物消耗也会增加呢
Dialogue: 0,0:15:02.90,0:15:07.16,Nadeshiko,Nadeshiko,0,0,0,,话说回来 静留你为什么会想去池袋呢？
Dialogue: 0,0:15:07.37,0:15:10.61,Shizuru,Shizuru,0,0,0,,那种事 这么直接地问我 我也…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:10.73,0:15:12.29,Nadeshiko,Nadeshiko,0,0,0,,是为了叶香对吧？
Dialogue: 0,0:15:13.32,0:15:15.22,Reimi,Reimi,0,0,0,,因为找遍吾野也没找到她？
Dialogue: 0,0:15:15.50,0:15:17.82,Akira,Akira,0,0,0,,玲实 你这说话方式
Dialogue: 0,0:15:17.82,0:15:19.09,Reimi,Reimi,0,0,0,,怎么了嘛 有什么不对吗
Dialogue: 0,0:15:19.28,0:15:20.77,Reimi,Reimi,0,0,0,,没错吧 静留
Dialogue: 0,0:15:21.00,0:15:22.76,Shizuru,Shizuru,0,0,0,,虽然是这样啦…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:22.84,0:15:24.72,Nadeshiko,Nadeshiko,0,0,0,,因为你在报纸的照片上看到她了？
Dialogue: 0,0:15:24.94,0:15:26.98,Shizuru,Shizuru,0,0,0,,嘛 差不多吧
Dialogue: 0,0:15:27.28,0:15:29.37,Akira,Akira,0,0,0,,诶…但是 你要怎么找到她呢
Dialogue: 0,0:15:29.42,0:15:30.28,Akira,Akira,0,0,0,,感觉不太可能吧
Dialogue: 0,0:15:30.38,0:15:31.34,Reimi,Reimi,0,0,0,,谁知道呢
Dialogue: 0,0:15:31.34,0:15:33.10,Reimi,Reimi,0,0,0,,说不定我们到池袋后没多久
Dialogue: 0,0:15:33.17,0:15:36.29,Reimi,Reimi,0,0,0,,叶香就会一边说着「好久不见！」一边过来了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:36.34,0:15:37.38,Akira,Akira,0,0,0,,说～的～是～呢～
Dialogue: 0,0:15:37.40,0:15:39.05,Akira,Akira,0,0,0,,是～这～样～就～好～了～呢～
Dialogue: 0,0:15:40.13,0:15:41.88,Nadeshiko,Nadeshiko,0,0,0,,那个 静留
Dialogue: 0,0:15:42.06,0:15:45.55,Nadeshiko,Nadeshiko,0,0,0,,如果静留你也什么都不说 就离开吾野的话
Dialogue: 0,0:15:45.55,0:15:51.78,Nadeshiko,Nadeshiko,0,0,0,,大家可能会像叶香突然消失之于你那样伤心哦
Dialogue: 0,0:15:52.04,0:15:55.13,Shizuru,Shizuru,0,0,0,,呃 这样吗 我没考虑到这点
Dialogue: 0,0:15:55.32,0:15:55.98,Shizuru,Shizuru,0,0,0,,对不起
Dialogue: 0,0:15:57.24,0:15:59.21,Nadeshiko,Nadeshiko,0,0,0,,还有一件事要道歉吧
Dialogue: 0,0:15:59.21,0:15:59.59,Shizuru,Shizuru,0,0,0,,诶？
Dialogue: 0,0:16:00.44,0:16:03.69,Nadeshiko,Nadeshiko,0,0,0,,对说出「你们没必要硬跟着来的」这句话的事
Dialogue: 0,0:16:07.38,0:16:08.14,Shizuru,Shizuru,0,0,0,,对不起
Dialogue: 0,0:16:09.17,0:16:12.82,Nadeshiko,Nadeshiko,0,0,0,,和你一样 叶香也是我们的朋友啊
Dialogue: 0,0:16:13.12,0:16:14.07,Shizuru,Shizuru,0,0,0,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:16:15.24,0:16:17.10,Reimi,Reimi,0,0,0,,嘛嘛 这样不就行了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:17.21,0:16:18.44,Shizuru,Shizuru,0,0,0,,不 真的很对不起
Dialogue: 0,0:16:18.52,0:16:20.30,Shizuru,Shizuru,0,0,0,,我没考虑到大家的感受
Dialogue: 0,0:16:20.76,0:16:22.32,Nadeshiko,Nadeshiko,0,0,0,,你能想通就好
Dialogue: 0,0:16:22.40,0:16:23.09,Reimi,Reimi,0,0,0,,对对
Dialogue: 0,0:16:23.20,0:16:25.00,Reimi,Reimi,0,0,0,,既然这样的话就回吾野吧
Dialogue: 0,0:16:25.08,0:16:25.64,Shizuru,Shizuru,0,0,0,,哈？！
Dialogue: 0,0:16:26.34,0:16:27.31,Akira,Akira,0,0,0,,你是笨蛋吗
Dialogue: 0,0:16:27.48,0:16:29.13,Nadeshiko,Nadeshiko,0,0,0,,玲实你在说什么呢
Dialogue: 0,0:16:29.13,0:16:31.05,Reimi,Reimi,0,0,0,,诶？毕竟要准备好才行吧
Dialogue: 0,0:16:31.20,0:16:34.43,Reimi,Reimi,0,0,0,,衣服 食物 毯子 露营用品之类的
Dialogue: 0,0:16:34.53,0:16:37.33,Reimi,Reimi,0,0,0,,啊 带点香薰蜡烛怎么样？
Dialogue: 0,0:16:37.54,0:16:38.14,Akira,Akira,0,0,0,,哦
Dialogue: 0,0:16:38.14,0:16:39.10,Nadeshiko,Nadeshiko,0,0,0,,确实
Dialogue: 0,0:16:39.12,0:16:40.74,Reimi,Reimi,0,0,0,,睡眠不足就会有压力！
Dialogue: 0,0:16:40.80,0:16:42.42,Shizuru,Shizuru,0,0,0,,诶 等等 等下啊
Dialogue: 0,0:16:42.50,0:16:43.61,Shizuru,Shizuru,0,0,0,,都走到这里了还要回去吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:16:43.73,0:16:44.49,Shizuru,Shizuru,0,0,0,,太浪费了吧！
Dialogue: 0,0:16:44.69,0:16:48.09,Nadeshiko,Nadeshiko,0,0,0,,但是什么装备都没有的话会很不安吧
Dialogue: 0,0:16:48.16,0:16:52.21,Akira,Akira,0,0,0,,说到底 我就没同意过要参加这趟旅行
Dialogue: 0,0:16:52.38,0:16:55.77,Reimi,Reimi,0,0,0,,那回到吾野的时候 晶你就留下嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:16:55.85,0:16:57.62,Akira,Akira,0,0,0,,我才不想一个人呢！
Dialogue: 0,0:17:07.65,0:17:10.25,Zenjiro,Zenjiro,0,0,0,,小雪女士 抱歉麻烦到你了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:10.57,0:17:14.15,Akira,Akira,0,0,0,,那我要带上《高丘亲王航海记》
Dialogue: 0,0:17:10.57,0:17:14.15,annotation,Sign,0,0,0,,和第一集提到的《黑魔术手帖》一样\N都是涩泽龙彦的小说
Dialogue: 0,0:17:14.30,0:17:14.85,Reimi,Reimi,0,0,0,,那是什么？
Dialogue: 0,0:17:15.04,0:17:16.64,Akira,Akira,0,0,0,,玲实你不知道的小说
Dialogue: 0,0:17:16.64,0:17:17.48,Reimi,Reimi,0,0,0,,啊 这样啊
Dialogue: 0,0:17:17.54,0:17:21.39,Reimi,Reimi,0,0,0,,那我就带晶吃不了的墨西哥辣椒薯片
Dialogue: 0,0:17:21.53,0:17:22.76,Reimi,Reimi,0,0,0,,很好吃的哦
Dialogue: 0,0:17:22.76,0:17:25.05,Nadeshiko,Nadeshiko,0,0,0,,还要提交请假申请呢
Dialogue: 0,0:17:25.14,0:17:28.50,Nadeshiko,Nadeshiko,0,0,0,,或者说休学才对呢
Dialogue: 0,0:17:28.68,0:17:30.66,Shizuru,Shizuru,0,0,0,,那就出发了哦
Dialogue: 0,0:17:43.36,0:17:44.41,Reimi,Reimi,0,0,0,,怎么回事？
Dialogue: 0,0:17:45.17,0:17:47.12,Reimi,Reimi,0,0,0,,之前还不是这样的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:17:47.56,0:17:49.13,Akira,Akira,0,0,0,,水位上升了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:49.28,0:17:49.98,Akira,Akira,0,0,0,,为什么？
Dialogue: 0,0:17:50.06,0:17:50.72,Shizuru,Shizuru,0,0,0,,地图！
Dialogue: 0,0:17:50.80,0:17:52.60,Shizuru,Shizuru,0,0,0,,刚才那个奇怪仙人的！
Dialogue: 0,0:17:55.46,0:17:57.96,annotation,Sign,0,0,0,,监督水岛努自己画的
Dialogue: 0,0:17:59.62,0:18:00.59,Reimi,Reimi,0,0,0,,这是什么声音
Dialogue: 0,0:18:04.60,0:18:07.06,Akira,Akira,0,0,0,,啊 是摩斯电码 这是摩斯电码啊
Dialogue: 0,0:18:07.22,0:18:09.80,Shizuru,Shizuru,0,0,0,,呜哇！我拜托了小雪奶奶来着！
Dialogue: 0,0:18:09.97,0:18:10.91,Nadeshiko,Nadeshiko,0,0,0,,让她敲摩斯电码？
Dialogue: 0,0:18:10.98,0:18:13.06,Shizuru,Shizuru,0,0,0,,不是不是 是善治郎先生的事
Dialogue: 0,0:18:13.32,0:18:14.80,Zenjiro,Zenjiro,0,0,0,,怎么还没回复！
Dialogue: 0,0:18:14.88,0:18:17.61,Zenjiro,Zenjiro,0,0,0,,不是说好要每天十七时联络的吗！
Dialogue: 0,0:18:17.89,0:18:20.35,Zenjiro,Zenjiro,0,0,0,,「这里是吾野」！「收到请回复」！
Dialogue: 0,0:18:17.89,0:18:20.35,annotation,Sign,0,0,0,,监督为了节奏感\N剪掉了摩斯电码之间的停顿\N
Dialogue: 0,0:18:23.10,0:18:24.25,Shizuru,Shizuru,0,0,0,,诶？什么？
Dialogue: 0,0:18:24.34,0:18:25.79,Shizuru,Shizuru,0,0,0,,点 横 横？
Dialogue: 0,0:18:25.90,0:18:27.07,Shizuru,Shizuru,0,0,0,,稍微慢点…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:27.18,0:18:28.53,Shizuru,Shizuru,0,0,0,,「mo」是怎么敲来着
Dialogue: 0,0:18:34.02,0:18:36.74,Reimi,Reimi,0,0,0,,好快！你敲得对吗？不会是乱敲的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:18:36.85,0:18:37.64,Akira,Akira,0,0,0,,闭嘴吧你
Dialogue: 0,0:18:40.42,0:18:41.99,Zenjiro,Zenjiro,0,0,0,,「水位上升」？
Dialogue: 0,0:18:42.13,0:18:43.32,Zenjiro,Zenjiro,0,0,0,,说的是高丽川吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:18:43.90,0:18:47.86,Akira,Akira,0,0,0,,「电机浸水危险」「速去高处避险」他这么说
Dialogue: 0,0:18:48.00,0:18:51.16,Shizuru,Shizuru,0,0,0,,诶～？！所以到底要往哪走啊
Dialogue: 0,0:18:51.25,0:18:52.49,Shizuru,Shizuru,0,0,0,,现在糟糕了啊！
Dialogue: 0,0:18:52.60,0:18:53.02,Akira,Akira,0,0,0,,你等会
Dialogue: 0,0:18:53.02,0:18:54.81,Akira,Akira,0,0,0,,不能直接用口语回复啦
Dialogue: 0,0:18:54.85,0:18:57.08,Akira,Akira,0,0,0,,「前进还是后退」「请指示」
Dialogue: 0,0:18:58.96,0:19:03.54,Akira,Akira,0,0,0,,「吾野和东吾野的海拔根据国土地理院帽帽帽」？
Dialogue: 0,0:19:03.73,0:19:04.49,Akira,Akira,0,0,0,,「帽」？
Dialogue: 0,0:19:05.21,0:19:06.50,Shizuru,Shizuru,0,0,0,,五分钟到了！
Dialogue: 0,0:19:06.50,0:19:07.84,Nadeshiko,Nadeshiko,0,0,0,,静留 现在怎么办？
Dialogue: 0,0:19:26.22,0:19:29.08,Shizuru,Shizuru,0,0,0,,前进！
Dialogue: 0,0:19:32.84,0:19:34.38,Akira,Akira,0,0,0,,要来了！大的要来了！
Dialogue: 0,0:19:34.51,0:19:36.27,Nadeshiko,Nadeshiko,0,0,0,,冷静点冷静点！
Dialogue: 0,0:19:44.82,0:19:46.42,Reimi,Reimi,0,0,0,,加速！快加速！
Dialogue: 0,0:19:46.47,0:19:47.79,Shizuru,Shizuru,0,0,0,,在做了！
Dialogue: 0,0:19:56.34,0:19:57.03,Shizuru,Shizuru,0,0,0,,前进吧！
Dialogue: 0,0:19:57.18,0:19:58.09,Shizuru,Shizuru,0,0,0,,冲啊！
Dialogue: 0,0:19:58.17,0:20:01.30,Shizuru,Shizuru,0,0,0,,跑起来——
Dialogue: 0,0:20:20.52,0:20:22.19,Shizuru,Shizuru,0,0,0,,回不去了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:20:23.65,0:20:25.04,Reimi,Reimi,0,0,0,,但是 嘛 不也挺好吗
Dialogue: 0,0:20:25.45,0:20:26.29,Akira,Akira,0,0,0,,有什么好的
Dialogue: 0,0:20:26.42,0:20:27.78,Reimi,Reimi,0,0,0,,只有前进可选了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:28.80,0:20:29.46,Nadeshiko,Nadeshiko,0,0,0,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:20:30.28,0:20:32.06,Akira,Akira,0,0,0,,那香薰要怎么办？
Dialogue: 0,0:20:32.21,0:20:34.01,Reimi,Reimi,0,0,0,,到池袋再说呗
Dialogue: 0,0:20:34.19,0:20:35.34,Akira,Akira,0,0,0,,明明你身上只剩一千日元了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:34.19,0:20:35.34,annotation,Sign,0,0,0,,差不多五十元人民币
Dialogue: 0,0:20:35.62,0:20:36.95,Reimi,Reimi,0,0,0,,借我点钱嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:20:37.04,0:20:38.46,Akira,Akira,0,0,0,,不要 我才不借钱
Dialogue: 0,0:20:38.46,0:20:39.08,Reimi,Reimi,0,0,0,,小气鬼
Dialogue: 0,0:20:39.24,0:20:39.89,Shizuru,Shizuru,0,0,0,,喂！
Dialogue: 0,0:20:41.49,0:20:43.64,Shizuru,Shizuru,0,0,0,,你们真的要去池袋吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:20:44.85,0:20:45.56,Reimi,Reimi,0,0,0,,肯定要去的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:20:45.72,0:20:47.57,Akira,Akira,0,0,0,,不去也不行了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:20:48.01,0:20:49.13,Nadeshiko,Nadeshiko,0,0,0,,静留你呢？
Dialogue: 0,0:20:50.78,0:20:51.57,Shizuru,Shizuru,0,0,0,,我要去
Dialogue: 0,0:20:51.69,0:20:53.41,Shizuru,Shizuru,0,0,0,,我要去 然后和叶香见面！
Dialogue: 0,0:21:45.70,0:21:48.92,Reimi,Reimi,0,0,0,,是东吾野啊——
Dialogue: 0,0:21:45.70,0:21:48.92,annotation,Sign,0,0,0,,东吾野有接触网\N但是也不能用
Dialogue: 0,0:21:54.21,0:21:57.09,Default,Resident 1,0,0,0,,呀呀 欢迎来到东吾野
Dialogue: 0,0:21:57.14,0:21:59.12,Default,Reisdent 2,0,0,0,,外地人很少见呢
Dialogue: 0,0:21:59.22,0:22:00.90,Default,Resident 3,0,0,0,,是啊 是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:22:02.40,0:22:05.00,Default,Keiko,0,0,0,,在这里好好休息一下怎么样？
Dialogue: 0,0:00:17.34,0:00:19.32,op - j,op_j,0,0,0,,Ga-tan go-ton ga-tan go-ton
Dialogue: 0,0:00:19.32,0:00:22.71,op - j,op_j,0,0,0,,Shoo shoo train 終 終 トレイン
Dialogue: 0,0:00:22.71,0:00:24.56,op - j,op_j,0,0,0,,Ga-tan go-ton ga-tan go-ton
Dialogue: 0,0:00:24.56,0:00:27.46,op - j,op_j,0,0,0,,しょっちゅう 停止 停止
Dialogue: 0,0:00:28.09,0:00:31.92,op - j,op_j,0,0,0,,仲良くゆこう 電車乗って
Dialogue: 0,0:00:33.36,0:00:37.19,op - j,op_j,0,0,0,,大好きなもの リュックに詰めて
Dialogue: 0,0:00:37.63,0:00:43.92,op - j,op_j,0,0,0,,ほらここが始発駅
Dialogue: 0,0:00:46.03,0:00:51.46,op - j,op_j,0,0,0,,ラララ 知らない場所へ導いて
Dialogue: 0,0:00:51.46,0:00:57.42,op - j,op_j,0,0,0,,キミを探す旅へ出るのさ
Dialogue: 0,0:00:57.42,0:00:59.38,op - j,op_j,0,0,0,,Ga-tan go-ton ga-tan go-ton
Dialogue: 0,0:01:00.06,0:01:02.16,op - j,op_j,0,0,0,,ワクワクスル
Dialogue: 0,0:01:02.66,0:01:04.69,op - j,op_j,0,0,0,,Ga-tan go-ton ga-tan go-ton
Dialogue: 0,0:01:05.36,0:01:08.26,op - j,op_j,0,0,0,,響け ホイッスル
Dialogue: 0,0:01:08.26,0:01:13.36,op - j,op_j,0,0,0,,世界が脱線しちゃっても大丈夫
Dialogue: 0,0:01:13.72,0:01:18.22,op - j,op_j,0,0,0,,ワタシたちは進んでく どこまでも
Dialogue: 0,0:01:19.02,0:01:26.79,op - j,op_j,0,0,0,,次はどんな扉を開けようか
Dialogue: 0,0:01:26.79,0:01:32.10,op - j,op_j,0,0,0,,さあ 終わんない旅へ
Dialogue: 0,0:01:32.10,0:01:37.14,op - j,op_j,0,0,0,,Ga-tan go-ton ga-tan go-ton
Dialogue: 0,0:00:17.34,0:00:19.32,op - train,op_chs,0,0,0,,哐当 咕咚 哐当 咕咚
Dialogue: 0,0:00:19.32,0:00:22.71,op - train,op_chs,0,0,0,,咻 咻 train 终 终 列车
Dialogue: 0,0:00:22.71,0:00:24.56,op - train,op_chs,0,0,0,,哐当 咕咚 哐当 咕咚
Dialogue: 0,0:00:24.56,0:00:27.46,op - train,op_chs,0,0,0,,总是 停止 停止
Dialogue: 0,0:00:28.09,0:00:31.92,op - train,op_chs,0,0,0,,我们亲密地乘上电车出发
Dialogue: 0,0:00:33.36,0:00:37.19,op - train,op_chs,0,0,0,,将喜爱的东西装进背包
Dialogue: 0,0:00:37.63,0:00:43.92,op - train,op_chs,0,0,0,,来吧 这里就是 始发站
Dialogue: 0,0:00:46.03,0:00:51.46,op - train,op_chs,0,0,0,,啦啦啦 列车带着我们驶向未知的场所
Dialogue: 0,0:00:51.46,0:00:57.42,op - train,op_chs,0,0,0,,开启寻找你的旅途
Dialogue: 0,0:00:57.42,0:00:59.38,op - train,op_chs,0,0,0,,哐当 咕咚 哐当 咕咚
Dialogue: 0,0:01:00.06,0:01:02.16,op - train,op_chs,0,0,0,,心动不已
Dialogue: 0,0:01:02.66,0:01:04.69,op - train,op_chs,0,0,0,,哐当 咕咚 哐当 咕咚
Dialogue: 0,0:01:05.36,0:01:08.26,op - train,op_chs,0,0,0,,鸣响吧 汽笛
Dialogue: 0,0:01:08.26,0:01:13.36,op - train,op_chs,0,0,0,,即使世界脱轨也没关系
Dialogue: 0,0:01:13.72,0:01:18.22,op - train,op_chs,0,0,0,,我们会继续向前 不管去往何方
Dialogue: 0,0:01:19.02,0:01:26.79,op - train,op_chs,0,0,0,,列车的门扉再次打开时 那又会是怎样的世界呢
Dialogue: 0,0:01:26.79,0:01:32.10,op - train,op_chs,0,0,0,,走吧 踏上永不完结的旅途
Dialogue: 0,0:01:32.10,0:01:37.14,op - train,op_chs,0,0,0,,哐当 咕咚 哐当 咕咚
Dialogue: 0,0:22:10.53,0:22:18.17,op - j,ed_jap,0,0,0,,優しい人のなり方を 誰か教えてほしかった
Dialogue: 0,0:22:18.17,0:22:25.65,op - j,ed_jap,0,0,0,,頼れる人のなり方を 誰か教えてほしかった
Dialogue: 0,0:22:41.73,0:22:44.65,op - j,ed_jap,0,0,0,,雨に濡れて傘も差せずに
Dialogue: 0,0:22:45.56,0:22:48.38,op - j,ed_jap,0,0,0,,いることもどうでもよくなって
Dialogue: 0,0:22:49.37,0:22:52.18,op - j,ed_jap,0,0,0,,明るさが急に怖くなって
Dialogue: 0,0:22:52.69,0:22:56.45,op - j,ed_jap,0,0,0,,大丈夫じゃないよ 大丈夫じゃないよ
Dialogue: 0,0:22:57.24,0:23:00.68,op - j,ed_jap,0,0,0,,一緒に歩くの嫌になって
Dialogue: 0,0:23:01.28,0:23:04.65,op - j,ed_jap,0,0,0,,でもひとりでいたいわけじゃなくて
Dialogue: 0,0:23:05.04,0:23:08.35,op - j,ed_jap,0,0,0,,目を合わせて笑えなくなって
Dialogue: 0,0:23:08.93,0:23:13.70,op - j,ed_jap,0,0,0,,大丈夫じゃない それは大丈夫じゃないよ
Dialogue: 0,0:23:15.05,0:23:18.58,op - j,ed_jap,0,0,0,,何度 傷つけ 間違って 失敗して
Dialogue: 0,0:23:19.02,0:23:23.05,op - j,ed_jap,0,0,0,,優しさ蔑ろにしただろう
Dialogue: 0,0:23:23.38,0:23:26.65,op - j,ed_jap,0,0,0,,傷ついて 許して 許されて
Dialogue: 0,0:23:26.95,0:23:30.43,op - j,ed_jap,0,0,0,,お前は生きろと言われただろう
Dialogue: 0,0:23:30.96,0:23:34.35,op - j,ed_jap,0,0,0,,みんなひとりぼっちだけど 孤独だけじゃない
Dialogue: 0,0:23:34.78,0:23:38.26,op - j,ed_jap,0,0,0,,あなただけここにいれば 孤独じゃない
Dialogue: 0,0:22:10.53,0:22:18.17,ed - train,ed_chs,0,0,0,,多希望有人能告诉我 如何成为一个温柔的人
Dialogue: 0,0:22:18.17,0:22:25.65,ed - train,ed_chs,0,0,0,,多希望有人能告诉我 如何成为一个可靠的人
Dialogue: 0,0:22:41.73,0:22:44.65,ed - train,ed_chs,0,0,0,,任由雨水打湿自己
Dialogue: 0,0:22:45.56,0:22:48.38,ed - train,ed_chs,0,0,0,,也无所谓撑不撑伞
Dialogue: 0,0:22:49.37,0:22:52.18,ed - train,ed_chs,0,0,0,,突然对光明感到恐惧
Dialogue: 0,0:22:52.69,0:22:56.45,ed - train,ed_chs,0,0,0,,我很不安啊 我很不安啊
Dialogue: 0,0:22:57.24,0:23:00.68,ed - train,ed_chs,0,0,0,,变得讨厌与他人并肩而行
Dialogue: 0,0:23:01.28,0:23:04.65,ed - train,ed_chs,0,0,0,,但又并非是想要孤身一人
Dialogue: 0,0:23:05.04,0:23:08.35,ed - train,ed_chs,0,0,0,,我们视线相交 却无法展露笑容
Dialogue: 0,0:23:08.93,0:23:13.70,ed - train,ed_chs,0,0,0,,我很不安啊 这很不对劲啊
Dialogue: 0,0:23:15.05,0:23:18.58,ed - train,ed_chs,0,0,0,,我无数次伤害你 误会你 犯下错误
Dialogue: 0,0:23:19.02,0:23:23.05,ed - train,ed_chs,0,0,0,,那都是因为我忽视了你的温柔吧
Dialogue: 0,0:23:23.38,0:23:26.65,ed - train,ed_chs,0,0,0,,我受到伤害 宽恕他人 被他人谅解
Dialogue: 0,0:23:26.95,0:23:30.43,ed - train,ed_chs,0,0,0,,这都是因为你曾鼓励我活下去啊
Dialogue: 0,0:23:30.96,0:23:34.35,ed - train,ed_chs,0,0,0,,虽然大家形单影只 但这绝非孤独
Dialogue: 0,0:23:34.78,0:23:38.26,ed - train,ed_chs,0,0,0,,只要你仍身处此地 这便不是孤独
